432
00:30:44,522 --> 00:30:47,361
Xiao Lin, I miss you so much.

433
00:30:48,841 --> 00:30:50,442
You went overboard with your ads.

434
00:30:50,642 --> 00:30:51,802
That explains the view count.

435
00:30:53,402 --> 00:30:55,922
