461
00:32:12,282 --> 00:32:13,402
Look.

462
00:32:13,961 --> 00:32:15,241
Lend me some money.

463
00:32:15,642 --> 00:32:17,042
Instead of 1,888 CNY,

464
00:32:17,241 --> 00:32:18,322
or 1,118 CNY,

465
